Package: mighty
Title: ADaM Program Generation Through Declarative Specifications
Version: 0.0.0.9017
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matthew", "Phelps", , "mewp@novonordisk.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Nicolai", "Skov Johnsen", , "nosj@novonordisk.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Aksel", "Thomsen", , "oath@novonordisk.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Michael Hedegaard", "Thomsen", , "mhzt@novonordisk.com", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides tools for generating ADaM programs in clinical trials using a declarative approach. Users 
  specify what data structure and derivations they need through YAML-based specifications, rather than writing imperative 
  code. The package handles dependency tracking between columns and rows, orchestrates code components, and automatically 
  generates executable R programs for ADaM dataset creation.
